{"tid":291899,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【快的85折】運輸署：若無合理辯解，即屬違法","createTime":"2017-06-21T02:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T08:01:25.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f397248327fdd4acf95137125b4c8aa542f0e3f","tid":291899,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170620/large/1497952632_b75b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170620%2Flarge%2F1497952632_b75b.jpg&h=ce153ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電召車應用程式「快的打車」近日忽然於程式內加入「85折」選項，變相提供減價折扣吸客，只要用戶於備註中選擇「85折」選項，即可主動向接單司機議價。運輸及房屋局局長張炳良早前於立法會上已明確指出，「若有應用程式以提供車費折扣的選擇作招徠，證據確鑿，則屬違法。」<br />\n<br />\n運輸署回覆本報指，根據香港法例第374D章《道路交通（公共服務車輛）規例》（下稱《規例》），「的士司機、其代表或看來是代表該司機行事的人」，不得以任何方式吸引或致力吸引任何人，誘使他使用該車輛。違法者一經定罪，最高可被罰款10,000元及監禁六個月。<br />\n<br />\n署方指，按照以上《規例》，若的士司機、其代表或看來是代表該司機行事的人主動提供優惠或車費折扣作招徠，誘使乘客使用其車輛，「則不論是透過手機應用程式、電話又或以其它方式，已屬「兜客」行為，若無合理辯解，即屬違法。」<br />\n<br />\n執法方面，署方指，「每宗個案的實際情况，需視乎警方進行調查的結果。倘若有足夠證據，警方會考慮提出檢控。」<br />\n<br />\n快的發言人回應指，「快的是一個供香港的士司機和乘客使用平台，備註系統會自動顯示乘客的常用搜尋字眼，給予乘客多種選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n運輸署表示，樂意為手機應用程式開發商及的士業界，就推出符合法例要求的手機應用程式提供意見。因應部分手機應用程式開發商的要求，運輸署曾會見他們以了解他們的運作模式，並提醒他們與及的士業界在利用手機應用程式接受召喚時，要注意法例規定，不應鋌而走險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56853617&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56853617%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170620&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=0f168d06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56853617%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170620&h=1608a8d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56853617&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170620</a>"},{"pid":"481f0b0395ce5292c256f00d6f329c62b4c4d8f5","tid":291899,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:38:27.000Z","msg":"乘客講價好似唔犯法喎，咁都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efb967e4de422227a67dceeaee13ff04544bc4f","tid":291899,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:44:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19be70996fd79162043ffac8b8091b5d9f5a31dc","tid":291899,"uid":53619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"皆大歡喜都有著數關你運輸署咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617feff90f6b0fdc2bf56a02c1d65fdc3ae51309","tid":291899,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:59:17.000Z","msg":"快的你都敢搞<br />\n你仲人地係皇冠車行咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3354c537f5f29f8c7d518460a0f4086f49fa40e6","tid":291899,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:00:39.000Z","msg":"哂鳩氣啦...快的中資底你會夠膽郁?😂"},{"pid":"887347dcbe38ee69169bc1f2734484cbdd957a33","tid":291899,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"轉過頭就會跪低"},{"pid":"0038dd1890304624edecd9c7841951f8bde5c458","tid":291899,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:08:22.000Z","msg":"個名好支那"},{"pid":"2382ab766988e23c8b57525f362ea24b1ff860ed","tid":291899,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哂鳩氣啦...快的中資底你會夠膽郁?😂</blockquote><br />\n出口術啫&hellip;<br />\n點都要講下"},{"pid":"55a83f4f4547754bd5c10a5887726a5c82e5d924","tid":291899,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個名好支那</blockquote><br />\n支那野"},{"pid":"8ceb3a98e8358c999d25bafb15171c7fa9a8c5d6","tid":